# game/script.rpy:169
translate chinese start_27094a2d:

    # "Hello there!" with dissolve
    "你好吗!" with dissolve

# game/script.rpy:171
translate chinese start_5f5bc83c:

    # "Before you continue, I just want to say a couple of things."
    "开始之前，我想说一些事。"

# game/script.rpy:173
translate chinese start_343fe138:

    # "First, I want to thank you for downloading my game. I started it as a personal project, and I hope that I will be able to continue with it because frankly I'm having so much fun doing it."
    "首先，我想感谢你们下载了我的游戏。 这是一个完全由我个人计划并制作的游戏, 而且我希望我能继续做下去，因为坦白说我做这个游戏真的非常的开心。"

# game/script.rpy:175
translate chinese start_8a419f09:

    # "That being said, just a few comments about the game."
    "话虽如此，这只是我对这个游戏的一些前言，我自己想随便说说的话（这个中文版花了不少时间，文本量很大而且完全没有机翻，希望更多的中国玩家可以来patreon上来支持一下）。"

# game/script.rpy:183
translate chinese start_5416e7f8:

    # "There may be one"
    "在游戏中可能会有一个"

# game/script.rpy:185
translate chinese start_1accf7cb:

    # "There may be one, two"
    "一个两个"

# game/script.rpy:187
translate chinese start_2f4053e5:

    # "There may be one, two, three"
    "两个三个"

# game/script.rpy:189
translate chinese start_54d1cc53:

    # "There may be one, two, three, four"
    "三个四个"

# game/script.rpy:191
translate chinese start_ef895c05:

    # "There may be one, two, three, four or more answers."
    "四个五个，或者更多的选项。"

# game/script.rpy:194
translate chinese start_1ea39eae:

    # "Many of your decisions will affect your relationship with various other characters, represented by a numeric score."
    "每一个你的选择都会影响你跟其他各种角色的关系, 将会有一个数学形式的计分板来表示。"

# game/script.rpy:195
translate chinese start_9456ca87:

    # "You will be able to see, after choosing an option, if the girl liked it or not, as well as your current points with her."
    "当你选择完每个选项你都可以看到（不一定是立刻的）,那个女孩喜不喜欢它, 同样你也可以看到你的当前点数。"

# game/script.rpy:198
translate chinese start_a7db82ba:

    # "The red heart means you get points, which is good if you want the girl to like you."
    "红心代表着你得到了她们的好感, 这就代表着好事，当然如果你是想让这个女孩更喜欢你的话。"

# game/script.rpy:201
translate chinese start_15aef18e:

    # "And the blue one means you lost points, because she didn't like what you did."
    "不过蓝心就代表着你失去好感点了，因为她不喜欢你的所作所为。"

# game/script.rpy:204
translate chinese start_39e66d9b:

    # "The point system will determine if you'll be able to access certain events in the future."
    "积分系统将有着长远影响，决定着你在以后是否可以触发一些特定的事件。"

# game/script.rpy:206
translate chinese start_fc786104:

    # "You can check your current points with each of the girls at any time through the menu! You can also see if you're following a girl's route, or not."
    "你可以在任何时候在菜单检查你跟每个女孩的当前点数! 你也可以看到你有没有进入到那个女孩的路线。"

# game/script.rpy:207
translate chinese start_d7a695bb:

    # "Be careful! Any bad decision could divert you from the path!"
    "小心！任何不好的选项都有可能使你偏离某个女孩的路线!"

# game/script.rpy:211
translate chinese start_ef7a44b2:

    # "Here is where the text appears, along with the name of the person who is speaking. You can press H to hide the text box."
    "这里是文本会出现的位置, 上面有说话人的名字. 按H就可以隐藏它。"

# game/script.rpy:212
translate chinese start_3714ff0e:

    # "(If you see the text is in parentheses like this, it means that the character is thinking without saying it out loud.)"
    "(如果你看到的文本在这样的括号里, 那就表示角色并没有把它说出来而是只在心里想)"

# game/script.rpy:214
translate chinese start_0e613157:

    # "Ok, that's all folks!"
    "好了，杂谈就到这里了!"

# game/script.rpy:215
translate chinese start_10c2da23:

    # "I recommend playing with music and sounds enabled, it enhances the experience."
    "我推荐你玩的时候把音乐和音效都打开，可以很好的的提升游戏体验（真的很重要，里面很多有趣的设计）。"

# game/script.rpy:216
translate chinese start_643c1617:

    # "And keep transitions activated!"
    "还有保持过渡选项的开启（不要调任何设置里的东西就可以）!"

# game/script.rpy:218
translate chinese start_c567895d:

    # "Remember, you control your own destiny. Think before you act and be sure to take all the opportunities that are presented to you."
    "记住，你掌握着自己的命运。 做出选择前请思考好并保证你抓住每一个出现的机会"

# game/script.rpy:219
translate chinese start_7c1a3e65:

    # "Because some things only happen... "
    "因为有些事只会发生在... "

# game/script.rpy:224
translate chinese start_6fc80951:

    # "Once in a lifetime." with Dissolve(1.5)
    "一生只有一次的机会中（Once in a lifetime)。" with Dissolve(1.5)

# game/script.rpy:226
translate chinese start_bdb4e048:

    # "Yeah, that's the name of the game! I had to put it somewhere. It's likely to be the only reference in the entire game."
    "没错，这是游戏的名字!我必须把它放在什么地方。 这可能是整个游戏中唯一提及到它的地方了。"

# game/script.rpy:228
translate chinese start_4de2bc89:

    # "Well, I'm out. Bye!"
    "好了，我走了，拜拜!"

# game/script.rpy:235
translate chinese start_831dcc3a:

    # "Wow, [me]? Really? I'm not here to judge, but damn, your parents must be strange people."
    "哇哦, [me]? 真的吗? 倒不是我在批判你, 但是取这玩意, 你爸妈真是奇怪的人。"

# game/script.rpy:236
translate chinese start_fefc5557:

    # "Okay, okay, I'm just kidding, sorry, let's get serious. I'm really going now. Thank you for playing and enjoy!"
    "好了好了，我只是在开玩笑, 抱歉，说认真的了.我这次真的走了。感谢你的游玩，享受你的游戏吧 !"

# game/script.rpy:240
translate chinese start_10a06ffb:

    # me "My name is [me]." with dissolve
    me "我的名字叫 [me]." with dissolve

# game/script.rpy:241
translate chinese start_7ab6a419:

    # me "I haven't always had an easy life. In fact, one might say that I had a tough childhood."
    me "我的生活总是不那么简单的. 事实上，可以说我有着一个不好的童年。"

# game/script.rpy:243
translate chinese start_07e4a820:

    # me "Oh sorry, what did you say? That you want to hear my story?" nointeract
    me "抱歉, 你说什么? 你想听我的故事?" nointeract

# game/script.rpy:252
translate chinese storyyes_1cb66f38:

    # me "Great! Don't worry, I'll try to keep it short."
    me "太棒了!别担心,我会从简来讲的."

# game/script.rpy:256
translate chinese storyno_a08029ea:

    # me "Jeez, with that attitude you're not gonna make it through."
    me "天呐，这样的态度你是没法好好经历后面的事的。"

# game/script.rpy:257
translate chinese storyno_451c8c7b:

    # me "Are you sure you don't want to hear it?"
    me "你确定你不想听吗?"

# game/script.rpy:260
translate chinese storyno_4c29e717:

    # me "Okay, okay, let's get straight into the heart of the matter then."
    me "好吧好吧，那就直接进入关键部分吧。"

# game/script.rpy:270
translate chinese story_175f2237:

    # me "I used to live in England with my family, in a village near Birmingham."
    me "我曾在英国与我的家人生活，在一个伯明翰市（英国中部，不是美国Alabama州的那个）的小镇里。"

# game/script.rpy:272
translate chinese story_2e9960e1:

    # me "I used to live in England with my parents, in a village near Birmingham."
    me "我曾在英国伯明翰市的一个小镇里跟我的父母住在一起。"

# game/script.rpy:273
translate chinese story_fc9b7f6e:

    # me "Based on some videos I've seen, the house wasn't bad at all. We even had a pool!"
    me "据我看过的一些录影带里，那时候的房子真的很不错。我们当时有一个游泳池!"

# game/script.rpy:274
translate chinese story_5b6584e9:

    # me "It could have been a dream."
    me "不过对我来说那就是个梦而已。"

# game/script.rpy:276
translate chinese story_0ddf643c:

    # me "However, we had to move every year because of my father's work."
    me "然而，我们必须为了我父亲的工作而东奔西跑，每年都要搬家。"

# game/script.rpy:277
translate chinese story_001ec621:

    # me "This meant switching schools, losing friends, and having to adapt to a new place constantly."
    me "这就意味着转学，失去以前的朋友们，还必须不断地适应一个新的环境。"

# game/script.rpy:278
translate chinese story_152dcb43:

    # me "Thankfully, I've always had the support of my mother and my two sisters. When it comes to my father... well, let's say he's not the type of father who hugs you and tells you he loves you."
    me "还好，我一直有着我的妈妈和两个姐妹的支持。说到我爸嘛... 好吧, 他可不是那种会抱着你然后说孩子我爱你的父亲。"

# game/script.rpy:279
translate chinese story_92b0edd9:

    # me "Sometimes I spent days and days without seeing him."
    me "经常我会好几天都见不到他。"

# game/script.rpy:280
translate chinese story_b90cefcb:

    # me "But not everything was so bad!"
    me "但不是所有事都那么糟糕!"

# game/script.rpy:283
translate chinese story_618ed1bc:

    # me "My father works as a financial consultant for various companies, and he earns a lot of money."
    me "我爸是好几家公司的金融顾问，他因此赚了很多钱。"

# game/script.rpy:284
translate chinese story_122104b5:

    # me "He has never spent a penny more than necessary on me but at least I have never had anything crucial missing."
    me "他虽然从没给过我一分多的钱，但至少我想要一些东西的时候从来没有缺过。"

# game/script.rpy:286
translate chinese story_19c4bb5a:

    # me "I've always been very active, and I've tried tons of hobbies."
    me "我一直是个比较开朗活跃的人，所以我尝试过很多爱好。"

# game/script.rpy:287
translate chinese story_4390be01:

    # me "However, each time I tried something new, I would get bored after a while and just pass on to the next new thing."
    me "不过，我每次尝试新东西的时候, 我都会很快觉得没意思了然后忘了它就去搞别的新玩意了。"

# game/script.rpy:289
translate chinese story_2c98e46e:

    # me "I guess this pattern was partly influenced by our lifestyle, as we moved constantly. Every single year, having to start from scratch."
    me "我想这种性格一定程度上是受了我们的生活方式的影响的，我们不停的搬家，每年都是，然后我的一切又要从零开始。"

# game/script.rpy:290
translate chinese story_0973ccfa:

    # me "That was my life, until about 4 years ago."
    me "那就是我的生活，直到四年前发生改变。"

# game/script.rpy:293
translate chinese story_0c92b2ec:

    # me "Once again, we had to move again to another town."
    me "再一次地，我们搬到了另一个小镇里。"

# game/script.rpy:294
translate chinese story_8d5d602f:

    # me "But this time it was different. It was a medium-sized town called Mistbury, and I don't know why, but I liked it from the beginning."
    me "但是这次不同了。 这是一个叫做米斯特伯利（Mistbury 可能是彩蛋，意为迷雾埋葬之地）的中型小镇, 然后不知道为什么，但我一到这就喜欢上它了。"

# game/script.rpy:295
translate chinese story_71b0a945:

    # me "This time, it seems that we have settled here definitely."
    me "这次，似乎我们确定会定居在这里了。"

# game/script.rpy:296
translate chinese story_c11a5d0b:

    # me "Sometimes it seems that everyone in this town has a secret to hide, which I love. That makes life here more spicy."
    me "有时候感觉这个小镇上的每一个人都藏着什么秘密, 我喜欢这样. 使生活可能会变得更刺激些。"

# game/script.rpy:299
translate chinese story_e0dd3030:

    # me "And this is me."
    me "这就是我。"

# game/script.rpy:303
translate chinese story_335090e3:

    # me "However, my mother died in a car accident when I was very young."
    me "然而，我母亲在我很小的时候的一场车祸中就去世了。"

# game/script.rpy:304
translate chinese story_1549ba19:

    # me "From there, everything started going downhill."
    me "从那时起，一切都开始变糟了。"

# game/script.rpy:305
translate chinese story_e8b83b53:

    # me "I never had the chance to get to know her, since this happened when I was only 4."
    me "我甚至都没机会去了解她, 当时我才只有四岁。"

# game/script.rpy:306
translate chinese story_7e84fa14:

    # me "I can barely remember her, and the little I do know is thanks to photos and what people have told me."
    me "我几乎记不住她了, 唯一能知道的都还要从照片和别人口中得知。"

# game/script.rpy:307
translate chinese story_a1fe92b1:

    # me "After that, it was just my father and I."
    me "之后，就只有我和父亲两个人了。"

# game/script.rpy:308
translate chinese story_afd9d8ee:

    # me "However, he was never at home and I felt lonely for a long time."
    me "尽管如此，他却从来不在家，所以我很长时间来都是很孤独的。"

# game/script.rpy:311
translate chinese story_7bff2e7f:

    # me "Let's say he's not the type of father who hugs you and tells you he loves you."
    me "可以说他就不是那种会抱着你然后说我爱你的那种父亲。"

# game/script.rpy:312
translate chinese story_cc44a013:

    # me "Sometimes I spent days and days without seeing him, so I had to learn to fend for myself."
    me "有时我过着一天又一天地见不到他的日子，我就慢慢学会了照顾好自己了。"

# game/script.rpy:313
translate chinese story_dbc055ac:

    # me "But not everything was so terrible."
    me "不过不是一切都那么糟。"

# game/script.rpy:316
translate chinese story_618ed1bc_1:

    # me "My father works as a financial consultant for various companies, and he earns a lot of money."
    me "我爸是好几家公司的金融顾问，他因此赚了很多钱。"

# game/script.rpy:317
translate chinese story_122104b5_1:

    # me "He has never spent a penny more than necessary on me but at least I have never had anything crucial missing."
    me "他虽然从没给过我一分多的钱，但至少我想要一些东西的时候从来没有缺过。"

# game/script.rpy:319
translate chinese story_19c4bb5a_1:

    # me "I've always been very active, and I've tried tons of hobbies."
    me "我一直是个比较开朗活跃的人，所以我尝试过很多爱好。"

# game/script.rpy:320
translate chinese story_4390be01_1:

    # me "However, each time I tried something new, I would get bored after a while and just pass on to the next new thing."
    me "不过，我每次尝试新东西的时候, 我都会很快觉得没意思了然后忘了它就去搞别的新玩意了。"

# game/script.rpy:322
translate chinese story_3efd27be:

    # me "I guess this pattern was partly influenced by our lifestyle, as we moved every 1-2 years because of my father's work."
    me "我猜这大概就是受了我们的生活习惯的影响，因为我们每一两年就会因为我爸的工作而搬家"

# game/script.rpy:323
translate chinese story_001ec621_1:

    # me "This meant switching schools, losing friends, and having to adapt to a new place constantly."
    me "这就意味着要不断地换新学校，失去以前的朋友然后适应新的地方。"

# game/script.rpy:324
translate chinese story_0973ccfa_1:

    # me "That was my life, until about 4 years ago."
    me "这就是我的生活，直到四年前。"

# game/script.rpy:327
translate chinese story_0c92b2ec_1:

    # me "Once again, we had to move again to another town."
    me "又一次我们必须搬去一个新地方。"

# game/script.rpy:328
translate chinese story_8d5d602f_1:

    # me "But this time it was different. It was a medium-sized town called Mistbury, and I don't know why, but I liked it from the beginning."
    me "但这次不同了。 这是一个叫做米斯特伯利（Mistbury 可能是彩蛋，意为迷雾埋葬之地）的中型小镇, 然后不知道为什么，但我一到这就喜欢上它了。"

# game/script.rpy:329
translate chinese story_ae0d8433:

    # me "Soon after we moved, my dad met a woman named Carla. She had two daughters, their father had abandoned them years ago."
    me "我们搬迁以后不久,我爸就遇到了一个叫卡拉的女人。她有两个女儿，她们的父亲多年前抛弃了她们"

# game/script.rpy:332
translate chinese story_150f580c:

    # me "They started seeing each other and before I knew it the five of us were all living in the same house."
    me "我爸开始跟她约会，在我了解到这件事之前，我们五个就一起搬家了这栋大房子里。"

# game/script.rpy:333
translate chinese story_b135fa33:

    # me "I assumed from the beginning that she's in the relationship for the money. That's just my guess though, who knows. I’ve never felt confident enough to ask her about it."
    me "我一开始觉得她是为了钱才跟我爸结婚的。 尽管这只是我的猜想，但是谁知道呢。我从来没开口问过她这件事。"

# game/script.rpy:334
translate chinese story_c7d26403:

    # me "I mean, she's way out of his league. I guess she wasn't earning enough to take care of herself and her two daughters."
    me "我的意思是，他们俩根本不是一类人。 我估计是她赚的钱不足以养活她自己和她那两个女儿。"

# game/script.rpy:335
translate chinese story_43e3b31e:

    # me "Despite that, Carla turned out to be very sweet and in the last 4 years she has cared more for me than my father has in my whole life."
    me "尽管如此, 卡拉确实是很好的人在这四年里她对我的关心已经超过了我爸这辈子对我的关怀了。"

# game/script.rpy:338
translate chinese story_e0dd3030_1:

    # me "And this is me."
    me "这个就是我."

# game/script.rpy:339
translate chinese story_5d422e8f:

    # me "It took me some time to adapt to life here but the people of this town are nice. Now I'm very comfortable."
    me "我花了一些时间来适应这里的生活，但这个小镇上的人其实都特别好，现在我过得很舒坦。"

# game/script.rpy:340
translate chinese story_c11a5d0b_1:

    # me "Sometimes it seems that everyone in this town has a secret to hide, which I love. That makes life here more spicy."
    me "有时候感觉这个小镇上的每一个人都藏着什么秘密, 说实话.我觉得这样还有趣一些，使生活可能会变得更刺激了。"

# game/script.rpy:341
translate chinese story_7702887a:

    # me "About me: I'm a simple man, I like sports, videogames, and..."
    me "至于我，一个普通人，我喜欢做点运动，打打游戏，还有..."

# game/script.rpy:342
translate chinese story_023d6637:

    # me "Holy shit I look so evil in this picture, I hadn't noticed before."
    me "我去，这张照片怎么把我照的这么猥琐，甚至像个坏人，我之前一直没注意到。"

# game/script.rpy:343
translate chinese story_79dc01a8:

    # me "I look like I'm about to announce a plan for world domination."
    me "看着感觉我像是要宣布一个毁灭世界的计划了。"

# game/script.rpy:345
translate chinese story_b7b5cc4f:

    # me "Yeah this is better."
    me "嗯，这张看起来好多了。"

# game/script.rpy:346
translate chinese story_7da72375:

    # me "As I was saying, I like sports, videogames and streaming shows."
    me "我刚刚说到哪了，我喜欢做做运动，打打游戏，还有看看电视剧之类的。"

# game/script.rpy:347
translate chinese story_30ee1bbd:

    # me "However, between this and that in this town there is always some event to attend, some mystery to unveil, or some chick to stare at dumbfounded, I can't concentrate on my studies."
    me "除此之外，这座小镇上还总有些这啊那啊的活动，一些感觉像是未解开的谜团一样神秘的东西和一些漂亮的你会目瞪口呆的妹子在吸引我，所以我很难集中精神好好学习。"

# game/script.rpy:348
translate chinese story_0ae5d2f7:

    # me "This is my last year before college and if I fail to pass all the subjects I won't be able to leave."
    me "明年我就要进入大学了，如果我今年有科目不及格的话，我就得被留级在高中了。"

# game/script.rpy:349
translate chinese story_c58ddda4:

    # me "And I'll become a failure in my father's eyes and he will throw me out and disinherit me and I'll end up dying under a bridge with a needle stuck in my arm."
    me "这肯定会使我成为我爸眼中的失败者然后被他扫地出门，他肯定不会让我继承任何财产，所以我的结局大概就是吸毒吸死在某个桥洞底下了。"

# game/script.rpy:350
